div.p:
Austria-Hungary was represented by Csmeji, secretary of state;
                                        Edelmann, counselor of the department of justice; E.
                                        Touffer, director of the Central prison at Leopo-glova.

President, O. M. Björnstjerna, present minister of foreign
                                        affairs of Sweden and Norway; vice-president, C. Grot,
                                        Russia; M. Thonissen, of Belgium; G. F. Almquist, Sweden;
                                        honorary president, Dr. E. C. Wines, of the United States;
                                        secretary, M. Guillaume, Switzerland, with four
                                        assistants.
